{"tid":1445684,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家入一入，防止更多手足自殺跳樓！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:28:30.000Z","uid":78785,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9df124e14653417e466264c21f9ada316055ae22","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"請睇下以下呢一中幅圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://courage-counseling.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/se-undischarged.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcourage-counseling.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F09%2Fse-undischarged.gif&h=ebb6ae64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我地既nervous system。 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係經歷難處既時候，我地會處於Fight Or flight既狀態，會分泌壓力荷爾蒙等讓我地更警覺同對環境更敏感。而家手足們大部分都係處於呢種狀態，不論係夢遊定係無夢遊時都係。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個狀態，短時間黎講既話係幫到我地去面對眼前既境況，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但長時間黎講會對個人既精神同情緒做成好大負荷。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/childhoodtraumarecovery.com/wp-content/uploads/images111.jpg?ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fchildhoodtraumarecovery.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fimages111.jpg%3Fssl%3D1&h=46e4b95e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係極端情況下，為左保護自已，我地亦有機會跌去freeze既狀態，即係咩都唔理，斷絕與外界既接觸，進入迷糊既狀態，以防自既再受傷害。<br />\n<br />\n一個健康既情況之下，大部份時間都係係兩者既中間度遊離，唔會太緊張或絕望。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係我觀察到手足們好多都已經好累，想放棄</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而大部分人反應都係 頂住啊！加油，齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家都好想堅持落去，好怕失去香港。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係，呢種講法會令人覺得要一直處於緊張既狀態，不能有一刻放鬆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家其實可以轉下講法：<br />\n<br />\n抖下再出<br />\n<br />\n唔好再用勝、負黎講呢場運動，事實上係係絕對既勝 同負，只要我地一直係度，我地會一直發聲<br />\n<br />\n唔好再叫人堅持，叫佢去做下其他野，睇少d 連登同報紙，唔好睇咁密<br />\n<br />\nTG group 組織一d興趣group<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa7209c8f99f313df46145bdda3648d36fb29e7","tid":1445684,"uid":106701,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"真係，過咗今晚忽然無力感極重，好撚想死<br />\n但死咗都改變唔到任何野<br />\n<br />\n死都冇撚用，好撚攰"},{"pid":"67f8bdd545442b4e633129425eee44c7d9157447","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9fa7209c8f99f313df46145bdda3648d36fb29e7","tid":1445684,"uid":106701,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"真係，過咗今晚忽然無力感極重，好撚想死<br />\n但死咗都改變唔到任何野<br />\n<br />\n死都冇撚用，好撚攰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:28:54.000Z","msg":"係！要停一停！<br />\n<br />\n到文宣做野！<br />\n今日好多黑材料！！！"},{"pid":"9b9e93263f3d31e79355993d586159b711615bb3","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"caccdab9af5422ca24ec6d0abf7d9deefb2359a8","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"推到更多人睇到"},{"pid":"dc57ad79dadd2c86810308f1d4d53045700e7a9a","tid":1445684,"uid":211300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb76d6f1b8361c9baa4f95ba697b2e762a4747c","tid":1445684,"uid":5702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"我真係想死<br />\n我覺得自己好廢 都好想自己咩都唔識 冇腦 做一個犬儒 或者一隻大藍絲 我就唔會咁唔開心<br />\n<br />\n我個心係會跳一下 痛一下 上兩個禮拜直情坐係到都會心跳加速 瘋狂跳到150幾下..."},{"pid":"004c70dfea4ec69020e937101a2df34e0eca0a83","tid":1445684,"uid":300697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fa7209c8f99f313df46145bdda3648d36fb29e7","tid":1445684,"uid":106701,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"真係，過咗今晚忽然無力感極重，好撚想死<br />\n但死咗都改變唔到任何野<br />\n<br />\n死都冇撚用，好撚攰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:36:28.000Z","msg":"我們年輕，時間在我們這面。忍辱負重，臥薪嘗膽。"},{"pid":"d98f6bd78e6a58778c133b7cb2b369c5e22113dc","