msg":"要呀，呢個係長期運動，所以唔可以比自己一直處高壓狀態<br />\n<br />\n觀星運動係幾好，不過始終都係同個抗爭有關"},{"pid":"00c56596f7695c3708bcff9677886a410ad8e409","tid":1445684,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"滴水穿石<br />\n<br />\n[重要］請文宣/民間記者會立刻準備今晚黑警所有黑材料煲大佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee44b62276db79ca622ec35de86a9ce7b38dbfba","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74eede290c1ff43fa52c54a3fb1639a24a153d7f","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58519a02e1b657000a93615b11a4008b45609be1","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:51:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86a2309e2adb72acb0edd96fe90f26bf13d3103d","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eba85eab899dc37e9841e03a7a14d617e8917b7f","tid":1445684,"uid":232233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"記住&quot;鬥長命&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c5adda531e7632f9135180b49955d31c6bd60b","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eba85eab899dc37e9841e03a7a14d617e8917b7f","tid":1445684,"uid":232233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"記住&quot;鬥長命&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"都唔好鬥了<br />\n<br />\n鬥都有一種要意志高昂的感覺"},{"pid":"59bd052c71116d6ea4e0f6bce9fcc5a9576f9cf3","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c6bd92f4f01fe56b6678f7b82918