我朋友睇片睇到喊<br />\n我都迫佢今晚唔好再睇<br />\n早啲瞓"},{"pid":"c160039c70189911f657641a2c19e4df1d4d4cb3","tid":1445684,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9df124e14653417e466264c21f9ada316055ae22","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"請睇下以下呢一中幅圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://courage-counseling.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/se-undischarged.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcourage-counseling.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F09%2Fse-undischarged.gif&h=ebb6ae64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我地既nervous system。 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係經歷難處既時候，我地會處於Fight Or flight既狀態，會分泌壓力荷爾蒙等讓我地更警覺同對環境更敏感。而家手足們大部分都係處於呢種狀態，不論係夢遊定係無夢遊時都係。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個狀態，短時間黎講既話係幫到我地去面對眼前既境況，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但長時間黎講會對個人既精神同情緒做成好大負荷。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/childhoodtraumarecovery.com/wp-content/uploads/images111.jpg?ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fchildhoodtraumarecovery.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fimages111.jpg%3Fssl%3D1&h=46e4b95e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係極端情況下，為左保護自已，我地亦有機會跌去freeze既狀態，即係咩都唔理，斷絕與外界既接觸，進入迷糊既狀態，以防自既再受傷害。<br />\n<br />\n一個健康既情況之下，大部份時間都係係兩者既中間度遊離，唔會太緊張或絕望。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係我觀察到手足們好多都已經好累，想放棄</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而大部分人反應都係 頂住啊！加油，齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家都好想堅持落去，好怕失去香港。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係，呢種講法會令人覺得要一直處於緊張既狀態，不能有一刻放鬆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家其實可以轉下講法：<br />\n<br />\n抖下再出<br />\n<br />\n唔好再用勝、負黎講呢場運動，事實上係係絕對既勝 同負，只要我地一直係度，我地會一直發聲<br />\n<br />\n唔好再叫人堅持，叫佢去做下其他野，睇少d 連登同報紙，唔好睇咁密<br />\n<br />\nTG group 組織一d興趣group<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:33:21.000Z","msg":"巴打，過左今晚一定好多手足心理好受傷<br />\n一定要推或者出多嗥心態調整嘅post<br />\n<br />\n不要說推，請推以下<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內，極近距離開鎗<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n<br />\n文宣/民間記者會！！！！"},{"pid":"91496f8e911e9ab6cc29b632bb193eab1b1271ca","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b46918daeb8c1ede91700dc24311426852a3e22","tid":1445684,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68efa74585afe765577fd0cf045e16f6001a50f7","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c69db5c62df6ea622ed007dd7a73b0aa20360cb","tid":1445684,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:30.000Z","msg":"我認同太繃緊係需要休息吓<br />\n凡事物極必反"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者都要照顧自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"我朋友睇片睇到喊<br />\n我都迫佢今晚唔好再睇<br />\n早啲瞓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"或者聽日請個假"},{"pid":"7e92bf03058027372217e400d89702a7ecee47af","tid":1445684,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91496f8e911e9ab6cc29b632bb193eab1b1271ca","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b46918daeb8c1ede91700dc24311426852a3e22","tid":1445684,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68efa74585afe765577fd0cf045e16f6001a50f7","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者都要照顧自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"我朋友睇片睇到喊<br />\n我都迫佢今晚唔好再睇<br />\n早啲瞓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"或者聽日請個假"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"721嗰晚之後我都請咗日假<br />\n頂唔順"},{"pid":"030302d66e0c6f7ca40a01ffd82dec9a61723f7b","tid":1445684,"uid":151304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor