\n唔好再用勝、負黎講呢場運動，事實上係係絕對既勝 同負，只要我地一直係度，我地會一直發聲<br />\n<br />\n唔好再叫人堅持，叫佢去做下其他野，睇少d 連登同報紙，唔好睇咁密<br />\n<br />\nTG group 組織一d興趣group<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:33:21.000Z","msg":"巴打，過左今晚一定好多手足心理好受傷<br />\n一定要推或者出多嗥心態調整嘅post<br />\n<br />\n不要說推，請推以下<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內，極近距離開鎗<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n<br />\n文宣/民間記者會！！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"好！我會考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3d266f934a577fbe9bddf75abce385248ea9f7","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b607d5f50561b4b5467c48b0926137b7a9f1b5cd","tid":1445684,"uid":296528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:38:00.000Z","msg":"我反而係想放自己血 用嚟寫血書 落佢地降頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e27d64e62b44480126f43160a9ed7ff7b80596c","tid":1445684,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:08.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"416880e4d987fc52a74e06ac1f39744304982477","tid":1445684,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:46:42.000Z","msg":"不要說推，請推以下<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內，極近距離開鎗<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會